{
  "stem": "13469.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we all had to come out in this assembly yard, very early in the morning, something like 5:00 or 6:00 in the morning, to be counted.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we had to stand in rows of five.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and we would stand there whilst the Jewish elders-- not even [INAUDIBLE], himself, but his underlings-- we didn't have kapos, like they have these, and brutal people that were set on in Auschwitz and all the other concentration camps to administer laws.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't remember that we had kapos in our section, but we had Jews who, again, administered all the rules that the SS laid down.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It wasn't really a Jewish council-- as I said, it was Albala who was chief in our star camp, and [?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Weiss ?] was his deputy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they had people under them who would organize the counting.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because the counting was very difficult.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "First of all, they had to count almost 4,000 people standing there early in the morning, and that alone was difficult.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But then, certain people were excused from coming to the appel-- people who had young children below a certain age, these women were allowed to stay in their barracks.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So they had to be counted in their barracks with these young children.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then there were people who felt ill, and they would come out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So they had to be counted in their barracks, and there were 12 barracks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Then there were people who were in the hospital, they had to be counted in hospital.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And all these separate counts, in the end, had to come to exactly the right number-- 4,174-- which the SS said that should be there.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
